      <title>乌克兰以预算“高度不确定性”为由，请求捐助者立即提供资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2023-12-28/funding-for-ukraine-pm-asks-donors-for-prompt-payments-on-budget-uncertainty</link>
